org.cloudgraph.hbase.graph

Class ExternalEdgeRecognizerContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudgraph.hbase.graph.ExternalEdgeRecognizerContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EvaluationContext

    public class ExternalEdgeRecognizerContext
extends java.lang.Object
implements EvaluationContext
    Context which supports the evaluation and "recognition" of a given external reference or row-key by a binary expression tree.

    A sequence uniquely identifies an data graph entity within a local or distributed data graph and is mapped internally to provide global uniqueness.

    Since:
    1.0.4
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
    See Also:
    HBaseGraphAssembler, GraphSliceSupport, CompositeRowKeyReader
